{"tid":761662,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【明搶飯碗】習近平結束外訪回國，李克強高調搶先會見英國外相，又聽取疫苗造假調查匯報","createTime":"2018-07-30T14:35:41.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-31T09:15:13.000Z","uid":155095,"like":7,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"f1165b68c7a7b782b1db938ab1cc29c2781af10c","tid":761662,"uid":155095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T14:35:41.000Z","msg":"總理李克強會見上任後首次訪華的英國外相侯俊偉，強調中英雙邊關係重要。 李克強表示，合作不僅有利中英兩國，亦對全世界有利。 侯俊偉就表示，英國「脫歐」談判預計十月完成，由現在到十月，他只到訪歐洲以外兩個國家，首先訪問的正是中國。他又提到，中英關係「黃金時代」發展良好，雙方可以有更多合作。<br />\n<br />\nsource: <a href=\"http://news.tvb.com/greaterchina/5b5f1673e60383125ae936b3\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.tvb.com%2Fgreaterchina%2F5b5f1673e60383125ae936b3&d=rOai4qxVptJ7VVmcqwObHTA5unq%2FSd9ZKvr75NUD1%2F0%3D&h=b90c21f8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://news.tvb.com/greaterchina/5b5f1673e60383125ae936b3</a><br />\n<br />\n總理李克強，主持召開國務院常務會議，聽取長春長生生物，違法違規生產狂犬病疫苗案件調查進展匯報， 並建立保障用藥安全長效機制。<br />\n<br />\nsource: <a href=\"http://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?csid=261_341&amp;itemid=1021958\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FPage%2FZH-TW%2Fnewsdetail.aspx%3Fcsid%3D261_341%26itemid%3D1021958&d=rOai4qxVptJ7VVmcqwObHTA5unq%2FSd9ZKvr75NUD1%2F0%3D&h=23c50fd2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?csid=261_341&amp;itemid=1021958</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://m1.aboluowang.com/uploadfile/2018/0725/20180725025948188.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm1.aboluowang.com%2Fuploadfile%2F2018%2F0725%2F20180725025948188.jpg&h=e4c52b19&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f8ea3c6214f243ce9aa15c03c261ea70e940722a","tid":761662,"uid":63669,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T15:10:51.000Z","msg":"垃圾間諜外相<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 廢May快啲比人彈劾啦"},{"pid":"7f355d0b5bf13ed480df3c98a11dda4f2b9e77cb","tid":761662,"uid":119393,"like